The gentile has yet to learn that the Jew is naturally deceitful and thinks nothing of lying to his 
fellow man. The Jew will take the customary court room oath before aing as a trial witness. He takes 
the oath (knowing while he is taking it) he will violate it because within himself he does not believe he is 
committing a wrong. This is an inheritance. It is part of being a Jew. He is born and raised with this 
belief and this teaching is a part of his daily life - like salt and pepper on the American table. They will 
