The naive Gentile, to fully appreciate the statements made herein about the Jews, as a race, must 
live and work with them closely. One must observe them under all conditions and surroundings. 

Too often overlooked by the Gentile is the 'sitive evidence' that the Jew is not of the White 

Race. 

